---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Taller Automotriz San Martín · Taller familiar en Díaz Ordaz, Mérida"
  description="Padre e hijo, éticos y honestos: así describen los clientes al Taller Automotriz San Martín. ⭐ 4.6 con 51 reseñas en Google. Diagnóstico rápido y precio justo en Díaz Ordaz, Mérida. Escríbenos por WhatsApp."
  slug="taller-automotriz-san-martin"
  ogImage="/taller-automotriz-san-martin/img/foto_1.jpg"
  fonts="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Libre+Franklin:wght@700;800&family=Karla:wght@400;500;700&display=swap"
  favicon="🔧"
  themeColor="#1f4d2e"
  whatsapp={"https://wa.me/529993057130"}
  telefono={"999 305 7130"}
  mapsUrl={"https://maps.google.com/?cid=1665724318458468883&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA"}
>
  <main class="tsm">

    <!-- ============ HERO / LETRERO ESMALTADO ============ -->
    <header class="hero">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="sign">
          <p class="sign-kicker">Taller familiar · Col. Díaz Ordaz, Mérida</p>
          <h1 class="sign-title">
            <span class="l1">Taller Automotriz</span>
            <span class="l2">San Martín</span>
          </h1>
          <div class="sign-divider" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="line"></span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M21.7 15.2l-4-4a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-5.6-5.6L14.6 8l-2 2-3.4-3.4 2.5-2.5A4.5 4.5 0 0 0 6 9.7l-4 4 2.1 2.1 3.5-3.5 3.6 3.6-3.5 3.5L9.8 21.5l4-4a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 5.6-5.6l3.4 3.4 1.4-1.4-1.4-1.4-1.1 1.1z"/></svg>
            <span class="line"></span>
          </div>
          <p class="sign-tagline">Diagnóstico honesto y trabajo rápido, de padre a hijo — el taller de siempre en Díaz Ordaz.</p>

          <a class="plaque" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=1665724318458468883&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Ver Taller Automotriz San Martín en Google Maps">
            <span class="plaque-l1">Don Martín</span>
            <span class="plaque-l2">· padre e hijo ·</span>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a class="chip reveal" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=1665724318458468883&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <span class="star" aria-hidden="true">★</span> 4.6 · 51 reseñas en Google
          </a>
          <div class="cta-row reveal">
            <a class="btn btn-solid" href="https://wa.me/529993057130" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" fill="currentColor"><path d="M16 3C9.4 3 4 8.3 4 14.9c0 2.6.8 5 2.3 7L4 29l7.3-2.3c1.9 1 3.9 1.5 4.7 1.5 6.6 0 12-5.3 12-11.9S22.6 3 16 3zm0 21.8c-1.4 0-3.2-.5-4.7-1.4l-.3-.2-4.3 1.4 1.4-4.2-.2-.3c-1.2-1.7-1.9-3.7-1.9-5.7C6 9.4 10.5 5 16 5s10 4.4 10 9.9-4.5 9.9-10 9.9zm5.5-7.4c-.3-.2-1.8-.9-2-1-.3-.1-.5-.2-.7.2-.2.3-.8 1-.9 1.2-.2.2-.4.2-.7.1-.3-.2-1.3-.5-2.4-1.5-.9-.8-1.5-1.8-1.7-2.1-.2-.3 0-.5.1-.6l.5-.5c.2-.2.2-.3.3-.5.1-.2 0-.4 0-.6-.1-.2-.7-1.7-1-2.3-.3-.6-.5-.5-.7-.5h-.6c-.2 0-.6.1-.9.4-.3.3-1.1 1.1-1.1 2.7s1.2 3.1 1.3 3.3c.2.2 2.3 3.5 5.6 4.9.8.3 1.4.5 1.9.7.8.2 1.5.2 2.1.1.6-.1 1.8-.7 2.1-1.5.3-.7.3-1.3.2-1.5-.1-.1-.3-.2-.6-.4z"/></svg>
              Escríbenos por WhatsApp
            </a>
            <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=1665724318458468883&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="18" height="18" aria-hidden="true" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2a7 7 0 0 0-7 7c0 5.2 7 13 7 13s7-7.8 7-13a7 7 0 0 0-7-7zm0 9.5A2.5 2.5 0 1 1 12 6.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0 5z"/></svg>
              Cómo llegar
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- ============ 01 QUIÉNES SOMOS ============ -->
    <section class="sec" id="nosotros">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="tag reveal">Nº 01 — Quiénes somos</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title reveal">El taller de Don Martín</h2>
        <div class="nosotros-grid">
          <div class="about reveal">
            <p>Somos un taller familiar en la colonia Díaz Ordaz, en Mérida. Aquí no hay call center ni empleados que cambian cada mes: quien recibe tu coche, lo revisa y te explica qué tiene es Don Martín o su hijo — los dos dueños del taller.</p>
            <p>Nuestros clientes lo repiten en Google una y otra vez: trabajo rápido, honesto y a precio justo. Hay quienes llevan años trayendo aquí sus coches — <em>«siempre llevo mis vehículos con Don Martín»</em>, escribió uno de ellos — porque saben que no les vamos a inventar una falla que no existe.</p>
            <p>El taller tiene acceso para silla de ruedas, así que entrar a dejar o recoger tu coche no es problema. Si algo le pasa a tu carro, mándanos un WhatsApp o pasa a vernos de lunes a sábado.</p>
          </div>
          <figure class="photo-frame reveal">
            <img src="/taller-automotriz-san-martin/img/foto_1.jpg" alt="Automóvil atendido en Taller Automotriz San Martín, Díaz Ordaz, Mérida" width="728" height="728" loading="lazy" />
          </figure>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ 02 SERVICIOS ============ -->
    <section class="sec sec-panel" id="servicios">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="tag reveal">Nº 02 — En el taller</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title reveal">Qué hacemos</h2>
        <ul class="servicios reveal">
          <li><span class="pin" aria-hidden="true"></span>Diagnóstico mecánico</li>
          <li><span class="pin" aria-hidden="true"></span>Afinación y mantenimiento preventivo</li>
          <li><span class="pin" aria-hidden="true"></span>Frenos y suspensión</li>
          <li><span class="pin" aria-hidden="true"></span>Sistema eléctrico</li>
          <li><span class="pin" aria-hidden="true"></span>Sistema de enfriamiento</li>
          <li><span class="pin" aria-hidden="true"></span>Reparación mecánica en general</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="nota-acceso reveal">♿ Taller con acceso para silla de ruedas.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ 03 RESEÑAS ============ -->
    <section class="sec" id="resenas">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="tag reveal">Nº 03 — Reseñas de Google</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title reveal">4.6 de 5 en 51 reseñas</h2>
        <div class="reviews reveal">
          <figure class="rev">
            <p class="rev-stars" aria-label="5 estrellas">★★★★★</p>
            <blockquote>«Padre e hijo que conocen su profesión, éticos, honestos, eficientes y efectivos…»</blockquote>
            <figcaption><strong>Jaime E. Portas</strong><span>Hace 4 años · Google</span></figcaption>
          </figure>
          <figure class="rev">
            <p class="rev-stars" aria-label="5 estrellas">★★★★★</p>
            <blockquote>«Siempre llevo mis vehículos con Don Martin. Trabajo rápido y honesto. Lo recomiendo.»</blockquote>
            <figcaption><strong>Angel Magaña</strong><span>Hace 2 meses · Google</span></figcaption>
          </figure>
          <figure class="rev">
            <p class="rev-stars" aria-label="5 estrellas">★★★★★</p>
            <blockquote>«Muy buen trato, precios justos y calidad en el trabajo. Tu vehiculo se queda en buenas manos.»</blockquote>
            <figcaption><strong>Jesus Alonso Hernandez Espinosa</strong><span>Hace 2 años · Google</span></figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
        <div class="center reveal">
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=1665724318458468883&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Leer más reseñas en Google</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ 04 UBICACIÓN Y HORARIOS ============ -->
    <section class="sec sec-panel" id="ubicacion">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="tag reveal">Nº 04 — Dónde estamos</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title reveal">Calle 7, Díaz Ordaz</h2>
        <div class="ubica reveal">
          <div class="ubica-info">
            <p class="dir">Calle 7 #383-A, por 6 y 8<br />Díaz Ordaz, 97130 Mérida, Yucatán</p>
            <a class="btn btn-solid btn-sm" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=1665724318458468883&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Abrir en Google Maps</a>
            <h3 class="horario-titulo">Horario del taller</h3>
            <table class="horarios">
              <tbody>
                <tr data-dia="1"><th scope="row">Lunes</th><td>8:30–18:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="2"><th scope="row">Martes</th><td>8:30–18:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="3"><th scope="row">Miércoles</th><td>8:30–18:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="4"><th scope="row">Jueves</th><td>8:30–18:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="5"><th scope="row">Viernes</th><td>8:30–18:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="6"><th scope="row">Sábado</th><td>8:30–15:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="0"><th scope="row">Domingo</th><td>Cerrado</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          <div class="mapa">
            <iframe
              src="https://www.google.com/maps?q=TALLER%20AUTOMOTRIZ%20SAN%20MART%C3%8DN%2C%20Calle%207%20383%20A%20por%206%20y%208%2C%20D%C3%ADaz%20Ordaz%2C%2097130%20M%C3%A9rida%2C%20Yuc.%2C%20M%C3%A9xico&output=embed"
              title="Mapa: Taller Automotriz San Martín en Díaz Ordaz, Mérida"
              loading="lazy"
              referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
              allowfullscreen></iframe>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ CTA FINAL ============ -->
    <section class="banda">
      <div class="wrap">
        <h2 class="banda-title">¿Tu coche ya te está avisando?</h2>
        <p class="banda-sub">Escríbenos y te decimos qué tiene, sin rodeos y sin sorpresas en el precio.</p>
        <div class="cta-row">
          <a class="btn btn-dark" href="https://wa.me/529993057130" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp directo</a>
          <a class="btn btn-dark-ghost" href="tel:+529993057130">Llamar · 999 305 7130</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ FOOTER ============ -->
    <footer class="pie">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="pie-plaque">Don Martín · padre e hijo</p>
        <p class="pie-logo">Taller Automotriz San Martín</p>
        <p class="pie-dato">Calle 7 #383-A, por 6 y 8, Díaz Ordaz, 97130 Mérida, Yucatán</p>
        <p class="pie-dato"><a href="tel:+529993057130">999 305 7130</a> · <a href="https://wa.me/529993057130" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp</a> · <a href="https://www.facebook.com/TallerAutomotrizSanMartin/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Facebook</a></p>
        <p class="pie-mini">Lunes a viernes 8:30–18:00 · Sábado 8:30–15:00 · Domingo cerrado</p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </main>

  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "AutoRepair",
    "name": "Taller Automotriz San Martín",
    "telephone": "+529993057130",
    "url": "https://demos.ivang.mx/taller-automotriz-san-martin",
    "address": {
      "@type": "PostalAddress",
      "streetAddress": "Calle 7 383-A, por 6 y 8",
      "addressLocality": "Mérida",
      "addressRegion": "Yucatán",
      "postalCode": "97130",
      "addressCountry": "MX"
    },
    "aggregateRating": {
      "@type": "AggregateRating",
      "ratingValue": "4.6",
      "reviewCount": "51"
    },
    "openingHours": ["Mo-Fr 08:30-18:00", "Sa 08:30-15:00"]
  }
  </script>

  <style is:global>
    :root {
      --linen: #efe9dc;
      --linen-soft: #cdd2c2;
      --green: #1f4d2e;
      --green-deep: #163a22;
      --brass: #b08434;
      --brass-light: #d1a94f;
      --ink: #23261f;
      --muted: #5b6152;
      --line: rgba(35, 38, 31, 0.14);
      --display: "Libre Franklin", system-ui, sans-serif;
      --body: "Karla", system-ui, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: var(--linen);
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: var(--body);
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      overflow-x: clip;
    }

    .tsm ::selection { background: var(--brass); color: var(--ink); }
    .tsm a:focus-visible,
    .tsm .btn:focus-visible,
    .tsm .chip:focus-visible,
    .tsm .plaque:focus-visible {
      outline: 3px solid var(--green);
      outline-offset: 3px;
    }

    .wrap { max-width: 1040px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }

    /* ---------- HERO / LETRERO ---------- */
    .hero {
      min-height: calc(100svh - 38px);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 48px 0 64px;
      background-image: radial-gradient(rgba(176, 132, 52, 0.16) 1px, transparent 1.4px);
      background-size: 18px 18px;
    }

    .sign {
      position: relative;
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--green) 0%, var(--green-deep) 100%);
      border: 5px solid var(--brass);
      border-radius: 26px;
      box-shadow:
        inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14),
        0 20px 44px rgba(22, 58, 34, 0.34),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(176, 132, 52, 0.35);
      padding: clamp(32px, 7vw, 56px) clamp(24px, 6vw, 56px) clamp(44px, 8vw, 64px);
      text-align: center;
      overflow: visible;
    }
    .sign::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      border-radius: 21px;
      background: radial-gradient(720px 240px at 18% -10%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14), transparent 60%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .sign::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 8px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(239, 233, 220, 0.16);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .rivet {
      display: none;
    }

    .sign-kicker {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 12.5px;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--linen-soft);
    }
    .sign-title {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: var(--display);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      line-height: 1.02;
    }
    .sign-title .l1 {
      display: block;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: clamp(20px, 5.4vw, 32px);
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      color: var(--linen-soft);
    }
    .sign-title .l2 {
      display: block;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: clamp(38px, 11vw, 78px);
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
      color: var(--linen);
      text-shadow: 0 3px 0 rgba(22, 58, 34, 0.55);
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .sign-divider {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 14px;
      margin: 20px auto 16px;
      max-width: 320px;
      color: var(--brass-light);
    }
    .sign-divider .line {
      height: 1px;
      flex: 1;
      background: rgba(209, 169, 79, 0.55);
    }

    .sign-tagline {
      margin: 0 auto;
      max-width: 40ch;
      font-size: clamp(15.5px, 3.6vw, 18px);
      color: var(--linen-soft);
    }

    .plaque {
      position: absolute;
      left: 50%;
      bottom: 0;
      transform: translate(-50%, 50%) rotate(-2deg);
      display: inline-flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--brass-light), var(--brass));
      border: 3px solid var(--green-deep);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 9px 20px 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(22, 58, 34, 0.35), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
      text-decoration: none;
      z-index: 3;
      transition: transform 0.15s ease;
    }
    .plaque:hover { transform: translate(-50%, 50%) rotate(0deg); }
    .plaque-l1 {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 15.5px;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--ink);
    }
    .plaque-l2 {
      font-family: var(--body);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 10.5px;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--green-deep);
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 22px;
      margin-top: clamp(36px, 8vw, 48px);
    }

    .chip {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      border: 2px solid var(--green);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 8px 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--green);
      text-decoration: none;
      background: rgba(31, 77, 46, 0.05);
    }
    .chip .star { color: var(--brass); }
    .chip:hover { background: rgba(31, 77, 46, 0.1); }

    .cta-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; gap: 12px; }
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 16.5px;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 15px 26px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      transition: transform 0.15s ease, background-color 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;
    }
    .btn:active { transform: scale(0.97); }
    .btn-solid { background: var(--green); color: var(--linen); }
    .btn-solid:hover { background: var(--green-deep); }
    .btn-ghost { border: 2px solid var(--green); color: var(--green); }
    .btn-ghost:hover { background: rgba(31, 77, 46, 0.08); }
    .btn-sm { font-size: 14.5px; padding: 11px 18px; }

    /* ---------- TAG (etiqueta de sección) ---------- */
    .tag {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 12.5px;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--green);
      border: 1.5px solid var(--brass);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 5px 14px;
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      background: rgba(176, 132, 52, 0.08);
    }
    .sec-title {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: clamp(30px, 7vw, 50px);
      line-height: 1.04;
      margin: 0 0 30px;
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    /* ---------- SECCIONES ---------- */
    .sec { padding: 68px 0; }
    .sec-panel { background: #e6dfcc; }

    /* ---------- SOBRE NOSOTROS ---------- */
    .nosotros-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 36px; align-items: start; }
    .about p { max-width: 62ch; margin: 0 0 18px; color: var(--ink); }
    .about p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .about em { color: var(--green); font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; }

    .photo-frame {
      position: relative;
      margin: 0 auto;
      max-width: 340px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 4px solid var(--brass);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 32px rgba(35, 38, 31, 0.2);
      transform: rotate(1.2deg);
    }
    .photo-frame::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(31, 77, 46, 0.24), rgba(176, 132, 52, 0.14));
      mix-blend-mode: multiply;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .photo-frame img {
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
      object-fit: cover;
      filter: saturate(0.94) contrast(1.03);
    }

    /* ---------- SERVICIOS ---------- */
    .servicios {
      list-style: none;
      margin: 0 0 26px;
      padding: 0;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .servicios li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      background: var(--linen);
      border: 2px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 15.5px;
      color: var(--ink);
    }
    .servicios .pin {
      flex: none;
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--brass);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(176, 132, 52, 0.2);
    }
    .nota-acceso { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 500; }

    /* ---------- RESEÑAS ---------- */
    .reviews {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 18px;
      margin: 0 0 30px;
    }
    .rev {
      margin: 0;
      background: var(--linen);
      border: 2px solid var(--brass);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 22px 22px 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(35, 38, 31, 0.1);
    }
    .rev-stars {
      color: var(--brass);
      font-size: 16px;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      margin: 0 0 10px;
    }
    .rev blockquote {
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      font-size: 16.5px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--ink);
    }
    .rev figcaption {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2px;
    }
    .rev figcaption strong {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 15.5px;
      color: var(--green);
    }
    .rev figcaption span { font-size: 12.5px; color: var(--muted); }
    .center { text-align: center; }

    /* ---------- UBICACIÓN ---------- */
    .ubica { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 28px; }
    .dir { font-size: 17.5px; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 16px; }
    .horario-titulo {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 20px;
      margin: 28px 0 10px;
      color: var(--ink);
    }
    .horarios { width: 100%; max-width: 420px; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 15.5px; }
    .horarios th, .horarios td { padding: 9px 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); text-align: left; }
    .horarios th { font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); }
    .horarios td { color: var(--muted); text-align: right; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
    .horarios tr.hoy th, .horarios tr.hoy td { color: var(--linen); background: var(--green); font-weight: 700; }
    .horarios tr.hoy th { border-radius: 8px 0 0 8px; }
    .horarios tr.hoy td { border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; }
    .horarios tr.hoy th::after {
      content: "hoy";
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      background: var(--brass);
      color: var(--ink);
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 2px 7px;
      margin-left: 10px;
      vertical-align: 1px;
    }
    .mapa iframe {
      width: 100%;
      height: 300px;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 14px;
      display: block;
      filter: sepia(0.12) saturate(0.92);
    }

    /* ---------- CTA FINAL ---------- */
    .banda {
      background: var(--brass);
      color: var(--ink);
      padding: 56px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .banda-title {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: clamp(28px, 7vw, 44px);
      line-height: 1.05;
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      color: var(--green-deep);
    }
    .banda-sub { margin: 0 auto 24px; max-width: 42ch; font-weight: 600; }
    .banda .cta-row { justify-content: center; }
    .btn-dark { background: var(--green-deep); color: var(--linen); }
    .btn-dark:hover { background: var(--ink); }
    .btn-dark-ghost { border: 2px solid rgba(22, 58, 34, 0.5); color: var(--green-deep); }
    .btn-dark-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--green-deep); }

    /* ---------- FOOTER ---------- */
    .pie {
      background: var(--ink);
      padding: 44px 0 96px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .pie-plaque {
      display: inline-block;
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 12.5px;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--ink);
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--brass-light), var(--brass));
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 6px 16px;
      margin: 0 0 16px;
    }
    .pie-logo {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 24px;
      color: var(--linen);
      margin: 0 0 10px;
    }
    .pie-dato { margin: 4px 0; color: var(--linen-soft); font-size: 14.5px; }
    .pie-dato a { color: var(--linen); text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--brass); }
    .pie-dato a:hover { color: var(--brass-light); }
    .pie-mini { margin: 14px 0 0; color: #8a9280; font-size: 12.5px; }

    /* ---------- REVEAL (solo con JS) ---------- */
    html.js .reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(16px);
      transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
    }
    html.js .reveal.in { opacity: 1; transform: none; }

    /* ---------- DESKTOP ---------- */
    @media (min-width: 760px) {
      .sec { padding: 100px 0; }
      .nosotros-grid { grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 0.9fr; gap: 48px; }
      .servicios { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .reviews { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); align-items: start; }
      .ubica { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr; align-items: start; }
      .mapa iframe { height: 420px; }
      .hero-actions { flex-direction: row; justify-content: center; }
    }
  </style>

  <script is:inline>
    (function () {
      var d = document;
      d.documentElement.classList.add('js');

      // Resaltar el día de hoy en la tabla de horarios
      var hoy = new Date().getDay(); // 0 = domingo
      var fila = d.querySelector('.horarios tr[data-dia="' + hoy + '"]');
      if (fila) fila.classList.add('hoy');

      // Scroll-reveal (mejora progresiva)
      var els = d.querySelectorAll('.reveal');
      if ('IntersectionObserver' in window) {
        var io = new IntersectionObserver(function (entries) {
          entries.forEach(function (e) {
            if (e.isIntersecting) {
              e.target.classList.add('in');
              io.unobserve(e.target);
            }
          });
        }, { threshold: 0.12, rootMargin: '0px 0px -8% 0px' });
        els.forEach(function (el) { io.observe(el); });
      } else {
        els.forEach(function (el) { el.classList.add('in'); });
      }
    })();
  </script>
</BaseLayout>
